{"itemid":1983,"subject":"Black Friday Books","event":"It is Black Friday, the day when Christmas shopping begins in earnest.\r\n\r\nSo let me say again: books make great Christmas presents, and autographed books are even better.   Being hard to fine and all.\r\n\r\nWe have a great selection at the Jean Cocteau Cinema, including two very special Anniversay Editions.   The GAME OF THRONES anniversary hardcover, signed by yours truly, and the OUTLANDER anniversary edition, autographed by Diana Gabaldon.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/401747/401747_900.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/400151/400151_600.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\">\r\n\r\nAnd if anniversary editions are not your thing, we've got all sorts of other signed books as well.  Here are just a few of those.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/397998/397998_300.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/398168/398168_300.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/398343/398343_300.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/398607/398607_300.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/399092/399092_300.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/400729/400729_300.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/399112/399112_300.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/399403/399403_300.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/399691/399691_300.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/400922/400922_300.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/401233/401233_300.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/401589/401589_300.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/400624/400624_900.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\">\r\n\r\nFor these, and many other titles, head to http://www.jeancocteaubooks.com/\r\n\r\nAnd yes, the JCC does now accept international orders... but you'll need to act soon (or pay a lot more) to get the books there by Christmas.","ditemid":507774,"eventtime":"2016-11-25 15:41:00","props":{"taglist":"jean cocteau cinema bookstore, signed books","crosspost_tw_log":"[Fri Nov 25 22:41:37 2016]R [Fri Nov 25 22:41:38 2016]https://twitter.com/GRRMspeaking/status/802281114521899008 ","homepage_reposted":63986505,"commentalter":1480361275,"opt_lockcomments":1,"crosspost_tw":"https://twitter.com/GRRMspeaking/status/802281114521899008","picture_keyword":"Spain","opt_screening":"F","likes_first_notify":1,"revnum":1,"interface":"web","personifi_tags":"nterms:yes","langs":"{\"languages\":[[\"eng\",0.623259632075625]],\"detector\":\"Lingua-YALI:0.015\",\"updated\":1480113729}","og_image":"http://l-files.livejournal.net/og_image/7059164/1983?v=1480361321","revtime":1480361314},"can_comment":0,"logtime":"2016-11-25 22:41:36","anum":126,"url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/507774.html","event_timestamp":1480088460,"reply_count":23,"comments":[{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/99074515/12922271","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/507774.html?thread=25314174#t25314174","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/507774.html?thread=25314174#t25314174","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/507774.html?thread=25314174#t25314174","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"seyera","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://seyera.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":25314174,"talkid":98883,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/5077